				Users must take in to account the length of the project and required working days, before any applications will be made and should they be successful they will be fully expected to participate as previously agreed on the application form
			</li>
			<li>
				Users are only allowed to accept one project from one project supervisor
			</li>
			<li>
				Users are allowed to submit multiple applications to projects, however if successful and choose to participate in the project, they must withdraw all other applications
			</li>
